    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>Crystal Field Theory (CFT)</h1>
            <p>Understanding Transition Metal Complexes for College Students</p>
        </header>

        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="index.html">What is Chemistry?</a></li>
